{"tid":1118213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【XXL Model】大碼衫店主創先河 募集重磅女模着靚衫「擁抱不完美地方，就是美」","createTime":"2019-04-21T08:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T16:26:43.000Z","uid":15333,"like":8,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"264a2a2f838e40d575f2f57936144030426b8db7","tid":1118213,"uid":15333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"玲瓏渾圓的身軀，姣好嬌俏的臉龐，貼地親民的素人氣質，一股「胖美女」風潮在台灣、日本、韓國席捲起來，身材苗條不再是登上天橋的必要條件；肥妹仔做Model，不再是癡人說夢。<br />\n<br />\n在風氣守舊的香港，一間大碼女裝店My Rules創先河，公開招聘兼職大碼模特兒，吸引500位胖女子應徵，最後選出四位素人，身材介乎L至XXL碼，個性各異，有嬌俏的可人兒，也有冷艷的性感尤物 。她們四人在鏡頭前搔首弄姿，除了是為大碼女裝店拍硬照外，還同時在挑戰社會「瘦即是美」的標準。「希望其他大碼女生，見到這些模特，會發現自己也能有扮靚的權利，藉此鼓勵她們。」店主Gloria如是說，更讓記者跟訪四位女生初試啼聲，記錄她們如何在鎂光燈下表現真我。而更重要的是，這班另類美女不是來展現一種高不可攀的美麗，她們不屑迎合瘦身潮流，想說的其實是：所有人都能定義自己的美麗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nv64kNG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNv64kNG.png&h=c7b8fa72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n店主Gloria（中）與四位準女模合照，她強調模特兒除了長得漂亮外，還要有一顆善良的心。當天四位女模初次見面，已能互相合作和補位。 (蘋果日報)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfORLeq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfORLeq.png&h=9cbae59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n採訪當天，女模首次拍攝硬照，店主找來專業化妝師和攝影師做形象指導。 (蘋果日報)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftEQ0NQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftEQ0NQ.png&h=d0ae05ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n形象甜美的模特兒Cherry說，自小已是肥妹仔，曾被同學嘲笑像「肥豬」，但一向我行我素的她未有介意太多，現在證明給人看，肥妹也有美麗的權利。 (蘋果日報)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tQB721g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtQB721g.png&h=5d9736aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外形冷酷的Kay曾留學外國，坦言大碼模特兒在西方國家早已是風潮，只是香港人較守舊，對肥胖女性仍有歧見。 (蘋果日報)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1frWWmm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1frWWmm.png&h=941285e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nChanhnez是ＸＬ碼模特兒，平日興趣是跳鋼管舞，是四人中最性感的女孩。 (蘋果日報)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UGFpkN6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUGFpkN6.png&h=16fcb3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLamLam是Ｌ碼模特兒，體型屬於「微胖」，形象可愛清純。 (蘋果日報)"},{"pid":"6a216d93a36bba4e2c2e6e02b854587cbc648c97","tid":1118213,"uid":22999,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"最尾果件可以一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a32a867c97f5918d0cc262979ee14b4896bb405","tid":1118213,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:57:53.000Z","msg":"Porkers"},{"pid":"c64aa29112c280ed9c0fb0469eeac8a7d6231731","tid":1118213,"uid":11301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:00:59.000Z","msg":"跳鋼管舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb027b9df317efe8ec372d462d27460222e732f1","tid":1118213,"uid":220435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:01:10.000Z","msg":"ok肥妹可以咁玩<br />\n咁肥佬呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8075ffa99cede56fd51014481d06cdedc8ac2892","tid":1118213,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:03:04.000Z","msg":"Lamlam我可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9547e27d7250d6893ee0099b574ec6465805b52e","tid":1118213,"uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:08:15.000Z","msg":"LamLam成個肥版有村架純咁"},{"pid":"0e37b1ef3a23bc86feff985c71222c4ded03d4db","tid":1118213,"uid":262,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:13:58.000Z","msg":"成日口講唔介意，明明自己先係最介意果個"},{"pid":"c8ae98aafbeca48969d23d5c230b6391936855e0","tid":1118213,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:19:19.000Z","msg":"長相甜美既欣直<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16fe62